1.first create two folders
    i. dist
    ii. src
2. run command on terminal npx tailwindcss init
3. tailwind.config.js file will be generated after running above command.
4. write "./dist/*.html" in content array
5. then in input.css file write three lines which are:
    @tailwind base;
    @tailwind components;
    @tailwind utilities;
6. Then in terminal write this command: 
    npx tailwindcss -i ./src/input.css -o ./dist/output.css --watch
7. then link output css file in index.html file